<div id="tt84" class="du-bgColor--gray-50 du-margin-top--12 du-padding--4 du-padding-desktopOnly--8">
<h3 class="du-color--coolGray-500 du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-letterSpacing--8 du-margin-top--0" id="p51" data-pid="51"><strong>見てみよう</strong></h3>
<div id="tt86" class="dc-columns-desktopOnly du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--gray-100 du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--6 du-padding-top--4">
<div id="f7" class="dc-column-width--oneQuarter du-margin-inlineEnd-desktopOnly--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--4">
<figure>
<a href="/wol/rslink/r7/lp-j?lang=J&amp;docid=502019187&amp;pub=ijwbq"><img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1283" data-img-small-src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1282" alt="" width="1200" height="675" class="suppressZoom" /></a>
</figure>
</div>
<div id="tt87" class="dc-column-width--threeQuarters du-margin-children-vertical--0">
<p id="p52" data-pid="52">聖書は，お金は悪だと言っているのでしょうか。</p>
<p id="p53" data-pid="53"><a href="/ja/wol/pc/r7/lp-j/1102021237/0/0"><strong>「金銭は諸悪の根源ですか」</strong>（jw.orgの記事）</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="tt88" class="dc-columns-desktopOnly du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--gray-100 du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--6 du-padding-top--4">
<div id="f8" class="dc-column-width--oneQuarter du-margin-inlineEnd-desktopOnly--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--4">
<figure>
<a href="/wol/rslink/r7/lp-j?lang=J&amp;docid=502019175&amp;pub=ijwbq"><img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1285" data-img-small-src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1284" alt="" width="1200" height="675" class="suppressZoom" /></a>
</figure>
</div>
<div id="tt89" class="dc-column-width--threeQuarters du-margin-children-vertical--0">
<p id="p54" data-pid="54">どんなふうに与えると神に喜ばれるでしょうか。</p>
<p id="p55" data-pid="55"><a href="/ja/wol/pc/r7/lp-j/1102021237/1/0"><strong>「与えることについて聖書は何と述べていますか」</strong>（jw.orgの記事）</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="tt90" class="dc-columns-desktopOnly du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--gray-100 du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--6 du-padding-top--4">
<div id="f9" class="dc-column-width--oneQuarter du-margin-inlineEnd-desktopOnly--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--4">
<figure>
<a href="/wol/rslink/r7/lp-j?lang=J&amp;docid=102015087&amp;pub=g&amp;issuesymbol=g15&amp;issuedate=201503"><img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1287" data-img-small-src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1286" alt="" width="1200" height="675" class="suppressZoom" /></a>
</figure>
</div>
<div id="tt91" class="dc-column-width--threeQuarters du-margin-children-vertical--0">
<p id="p56" data-pid="56">ギャンブルは害のない娯楽でしょうか。</p>
<p id="p57" data-pid="57"><a href="/ja/wol/pc/r7/lp-j/1102021237/2/0"><strong>「聖書の見方 ギャンブル」</strong>（「目ざめよ！」2015年3月号）</a></p>
